original_title: Alejandro Sanz: El Concierto Tour Más '98
overview: El Concierto Tour Mas '98 is a musical concert by Spanish singer-songwriter and musician Alejandro Sanz.  In mid-1998, Alejandro Sanz began his first international tour, reaching Latin America, the USA and other continents such as Asia and the United Kingdom. The Concierto Tour Más, was recorded at the Palau Sant Jordi in Barcelona, ​​on June 18 and 19, 1998.
title: Alejandro Sanz: El Concierto Tour Más '98
